<plot>The Pink Panther, who lives in a small, rundown shack in the middle of the city, finds a five dollar bill. He gets so afraid of thieves, he decides to bury the bill in the ground. Later he finds out that a hotel has been erected on the very spot where the bill was hidden. He sneaks into the hotel when a janitor arrives, and starts looking for the right spot to start digging.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?433384</url></doc>
